UID:PVh3ZAo3VMsrGEzOR8_Fw
SUMMARY:Norwegian Language Classes
DTSTAMP:20260403T051049Z
DTSTART:20260410T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:This nine-week series will allow you to jump into the basics of
	 Norwegian language and culture in a supportive\, face-to-face classroom e
	nvironment. Students will learn essential vocabulary\, everyday phrases\, 
	pronunciation\, and simple grammar structures through interactive activiti
	es\, conversation practice\, and cultural activities. No prior foreign lan
	guage experience is required\; ages 16+.\n\nEvery Thursday\, April 2 - May
	 28\n\nNOR1A: 5-6:30pm - NOR1A is for absolute beginners with no prior lan
	guage experience\n\nNOR1C: 6:45-8pm - NOR1C is for students who may know s
	ome basic Norwegian and want to grow their skills\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amc
	ity.com/events/#/details/norwegian-language-classes/18360479/2026-04-09T00
	\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/norwegian-language-classe
	s/18360479/2026-04-09T00
