	ental FIFA events\, it&'s crucial to align our regional efforts to maximiz
	e economic and infrastructural benefits. This meeting will gather key stak
	eholders from various sectors\, including our cities and business communit
	y\, to strategize and synchronize our readiness plans with an emphasis in 
	preparing our business community to ensure you are ready for this economic
	 opportunity. So do you want to learn about what resources are available t
	o you to maximize this time? Register to learn more now. These quarterly e
	vents are brought to you by the Seattle Southside Chamber of Commerce and 
	Explore Seattle Southside.  This meeting is a pivotal opportunity for stak
	eholders to collaborate and ensure our region is fully prepared to host FI
	FA events successfully. Together\, we can create a unified and effective e
	xecution plan that benefits all.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/
	details/global-soccer-game-webinar/17602992/2026-04-14T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday
